      "content": "i just tried to walk to the clinic but the sun is so strong and i feel like i'm gonna pass out if i move too much. i have some coconut water and some electrolyte tablets in my bag. if i just sit in the shade and drink these rapidly, i'll be fine right? i don't want to go to the hospital if it's just the heat.",
